Padre-Plugin-Debugger
=====================

This is a very early pre-release of a perl debugger for padre.


INSTALLATION
============

Padre has to be installed before installing this module.
To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

